source.name: City Of Seattle Parks
source.description:
Parks maintained or managed by Seattle Parks that are within the city limits.
Seattle Parks locations in the City of Seattle. Includes properties that are managed by Seattle Parks.  Also, includes parks that may not be a "park" but offices or buildings.
